  "text": "Spawn grains such as wheat, millet and corn have been reported to affect carpophores production [CITATION_1] and there are various additives that are known to stimulate fruiting. They include rice bran, cassava peels and soybean powder, [CITATION_2] examined the effect of spawn grains such as weat, millet and corn on the culture of lentinus squarrosulus. The results showed that corn spawn induced highest yield and dry weight of fruiting as compared to wheat and millet spawn.",
